State Regulations

The Fund will, within 30 days after adoption of this Part, file a copy of such Part, and any amendments thereto, with the State

Comptroller, the State Director of the Budget, the Chairman of the Senate

Finance Committee, and the Chairman of the Assembly Ways and Means
